metadata.name: Alien Ethalik
metadata.description: The planet ETH1.0, inhabited by Ethaliks and their weakening king gaPOW, are dying. Plagued by a scourge of creatures known as "beGAS", their FUD army pushes to destroy all life. A hero gaPOS emerges, with plans to seek a new home on ETH2.0 for the last of the Ethaliks. Join our fight!
